{"data":[{"date":"05:39 17/08","title":"Kh\u00e1m ph\u00e1 th\u00fa ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u1ed3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c HLV Premier League","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/kham-pha-thu-choi-dong-ho-cua-cac-hlv-premier-league.jpg","new_desc":"${8_news_content2}","new_url":"","id":"5576","checkdouble":"194635"},{"date":"05:49 17/08","title":"Man City ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u M.U trong b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u","type":"H\u1eadu tr\u01b0\u1eddng","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/17/man-city-che-gieu-mu-trong-bo-phim-tai-lieu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2017/18 c\u1ee7a Man City do Amazon s\u1ea3n xu\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu. Trong \u0111\u00f3 c\u00f3 \u0111o\u1ea1n Man City ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u M.U sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Old Trafford.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">V\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 T\u01b0 ng\u00e0y 15/8 theo gi\u1edd Anh, Amazon \u0111\u00e3 cho c\u00f4ng chi\u1ebfu b\u1ed9 phim t\u00e0i li\u1ec7u v\u1ec1 Man City n\u1eb1m trong series ch\u01b0\u01a1ng tr\u00ecnh \u201cAll Or Nothing\u201d. V\u1edbi chi ph\u00ed 10 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng cho Man City, Amazon \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn s\u00e2u v\u00e0 ghi l\u1ea1i nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb c\u1ee7a n\u1eeda xanh th\u00e0nh Manchester trong m\u00f9a 2017/18 \u2013 m\u00f9a m\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Pep Guardiola l\u00ean ng\u00f4i t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u1edbi v\u00f4 s\u1ed1 nh\u1eefng k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\" title=\"\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/mancity.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eadp th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 phim n\u00e0y t\u1eadp trung v\u00e0o chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Man City tr\u01b0\u1edbc M.U \u1edf s\u00e2n Old Trafford v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 12/2017, t\u1eeb \u0111\u00f3 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Guardiola l\u1eadp k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp t\u1ea1i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh d\u00e0i nh\u1ea5t (14 tr\u1eadn, sau n\u00e0y n\u00e2ng l\u00ean th\u00e0nh 18 tr\u1eadn). <br>\r\n<br>\r\nGuardiola ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i M.U: \u201cC\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 gi\u1ebft h\u1ecd (M.U) trong khi ch\u01a1i th\u1ee9 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n th\u1eadt xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc. Ch\u00fang ta h\u00e0nh qu\u00e2n \u0111\u1ebfn s\u00e2n c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m v\u00e0 cho h\u1ecd th\u1ea5y Man City l\u00e0 ai. C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111ang n\u1eb1m trong tay ch\u00fang ta. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 ch\u00ednh Man City m\u1edbi c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ng\u0103n Man City v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 phim c\u0169ng chi\u1ebfu l\u1ea1i c\u1ea3nh fan Man City n\u00e1n l\u1ea1i kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i Old Trafford \u0111\u1ec3 h\u00e1t ch\u1ebf gi\u1ec5u M.U v\u1edbi ca t\u1eeb \u201cpark the bus\u201d \u2013 \u00e1m ch\u1ec9 c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1eadu xe bu\u00fdt tr\u01b0\u1edbc khung th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Jose Mourinho. Trong qu\u00e1 tr\u00ecnh x\u00e2y d\u1ef1ng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n cho tr\u1eadn derby Manchester, Pep v\u00e0 tr\u1ee3 l\u00fd \u0111\u00e3 ph\u00e2n t\u00edch \u0111i\u1ec3m y\u1ebfu \u1edf c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u1ee7a Qu\u1ef7 \u0111\u1ecf. Qu\u1ea3 th\u1eadt sau \u0111\u00f3, Man City ghi 2 b\u00e0n t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a David Silva v\u00e0 Nicolas Otamendi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nDe Bruyne ch\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1ng \u0111i xem bu\u1ed5i c\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n<br>\r\nDe Bruyne ch\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1ng \u0111i xem bu\u1ed5i c\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nKevin de Bruyne, ng\u01b0\u1eddi ch\u1ed1ng n\u1ea1ng \u0111\u1ebfn xem bu\u1ed5i c\u00f4ng di\u1ec5n c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00e0nh th\u1eddi l\u01b0\u1ee3ng ri\u00eang trong t\u1eadp \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 phim. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 k\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf Chelsea: \u201cT\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 20 tu\u1ed5i khi quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Chelsea. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u1edf \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t v\u00e0 ngh\u0129 m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n \u0111ang di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1eb9p. Th\u1ebf nh\u01b0ng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y, m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ed9 phim c\u0169ng ghi l\u1ea1i kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc Benjamin Mendy khi anh nghe b\u00e1c s\u0129 Ramon Cugat th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o s\u1ebd b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 ph\u1ea7n c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Sergio Aguero ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t trong 2 ng\u01b0\u1eddi b\u1ea1n th\u00e2n l\u00e0 th\u1ee7 th\u00e0nh David de Gea c\u1ee7a M.U. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o ng\u01b0\u1eddi Argentina chia s\u1ebb con trai Benjamin c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn s\u1ed1ng \u1edf Argentina v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ebfn Anh th\u0103m b\u1ed1 1 tu\u1ea7n trong m\u1ed7i th\u00e1ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nAguero n\u00f3i: \u201cPh\u1ea7n l\u1edbn th\u1eddi gian t\u00f4i s\u1ed1ng m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh. N\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111i ch\u01a1i c\u00f9ng Otamendi ho\u1eb7c De Gea. T\u00f4i th\u00e2n v\u1edbi De Gea v\u00ec ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u00f9ng nhau t\u1ea1i Atletico Madrid. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 t\u00ecnh b\u1ea1n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb th\u1eddi \u1edf Atletico nh\u01b0ng anh \u1ea5y ch\u01a1i cho M.U c\u00f2n t\u00f4i l\u00e0 City\u201d.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5575","checkdouble":"194636"},{"date":"06:51 17/08","title":"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft Serie A v\u00e0o cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Italia","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-chua-the-ra-mat-serie-a-vao-cuoi-tuan-nay.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u1ed3ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t l\u00f9i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00ec th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u Genoa h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba qua.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Theo l\u1ecbch, cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y Serie A 2018/19 s\u1ebd ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c kh\u1edfi tranh v\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta \u0111ang ch\u1edd \u0111\u1ee3i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ra m\u1eaft ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u1ee7a Ronaldo trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o Juventus va c\u0169ng l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a anh trong s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p t\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ea5p CLB s\u1ed1 1 Italia. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 b\u1ecb tr\u00ec ho\u00e3n do th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch s\u1eadp c\u1ea7u h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 Ba v\u1eeba qua.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft, v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 201819 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Si\u00eau sao Ronaldo ch\u01b0a th\u1ec3 ra m\u1eaft, v\u00f2ng 1 Serie A 201819 b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/sieu-sao-ronaldo-lai-ghi-ban-trong-mau-ao-juventus.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u00a0</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nV\u1ee5 s\u1ee5p \u0111\u1ed5 c\u00e2y c\u1ea7u cao t\u1ed1c \u1edf Genoa \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn 39 ng\u01b0\u1eddi thi\u1ec7t m\u1ea1ng. Hi\u1ec7n c\u00e1c c\u01a1 quan ch\u1ee9c n\u0103ng \u0111\u1ecba ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1eabn \u0111ang t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u00e1c n\u1ea1n nh\u00e2n c\u00f2n s\u1ed1ng s\u00f3t.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ea3m k\u1ecbch n\u00e0y, 1 s\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u1edf Serie A \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 xu\u1ea5t BTC gi\u1ea3i l\u00f9i l\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1eaft, 2 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Sampdoria - Fiorentina v\u00e0 Milan - Genoa \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BTC \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd ho\u00e3n l\u1ea1i.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00eda Juventus ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0a ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o n\u00e0o nh\u01b0ng ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a Sampdoria \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn Bianconeri c\u0169ng s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y. Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sampdoria, Massimo Ferrero ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Agnelli, \u00f4ng \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Juve s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u. Kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u00e1 b\u00f3ng \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y. Th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra qu\u1ed1c tang\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong khi \u0111\u00f3, 1 tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 t\u1eeb Fiorentina cho bi\u1ebft: \"L\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u1ec3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 \u00dd d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i, th\u01b0\u01a1ng ti\u1ebfc v\u00e0 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng tang l\u1ec5 c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng ch\u1ee5c gia \u0111\u00ecnh. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u00e0 \u0111am m\u00ea v\u00e0 ni\u1ec1m vui nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. T\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i \u1edf b\u00ean c\u1ea1nh Genoa\".<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u01b0a c\u00f3 th\u00f4ng b\u00e1o ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c t\u1eeb Juventus v\u00e0 BTC Serie A nh\u01b0ng nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa L\u00e3o b\u00e0 v\u00e0 Chievo v\u00e0o \u0111\u00eam th\u1ee9 B\u1ea3y s\u1ebd b\u1ecb ho\u00e3n l\u1ea1i. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ed3ng ngh\u0129a, NHM s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ch\u1edd th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u1ea1y \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u1edf Serie A.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5574","checkdouble":"194644"},{"date":"22:05 16/08","title":"HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.\r\n\r\n</h2><h2><span style=\"text-align: center;\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif;\">&nbsp;</span></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba c\u00f3 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i ASIAD n\u0103m nay sau khi v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Olympic Nepal \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u di\u1ec5n ra t\u1ed1i 16/8. B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Anh \u0110\u1ee9c, V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp sau hai l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo v\u1eabn c\u00f2n m\u1ed9t nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Ch\u1ec9 khi l\u00e0m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y, h\u1ecd m\u1edbi tr\u00e1nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E, r\u1ea5t c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 Olympic H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Park Hang Seo\" title=\"Park Hang Seo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n<span style=\"font-family: arial, verdana, &quot;Lucida Grande&quot;, helvetica, sans-serif; text-align: start;\">&nbsp;</span></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e3 l\u00ean d\u00e2y c\u00f3t tinh th\u1ea7n cho c\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00d4ng t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: &ldquo;C\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u0129 \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u1eeba m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e1 xong v\u1edbi Nepal v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u1ea7n ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn c\u00f2n 2 ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb h\u01b0\u1edbng \u0111\u1ebfn tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. Hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. Nh\u1eefng ph\u01b0\u01a1ng \u00e1n \u0111\u1ec3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u&nbsp; v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ra sao c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u00ednh \u0111\u1ebfn&rdquo;.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb th\u00eam v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1eeba xong tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, \u00f4ng Park n\u00f3i: &ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac khi h\u00f4m nay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1edbm tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn. Nh\u00e2n \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u1ea3m \u01a1n \u0111\u1ebfn c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 \u0111i\u1ec3m quan tr\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal&rdquo;.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chung quan \u0111i\u1ec3m v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea7y c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng V\u0103n Quy\u1ebft cho bi\u1ebft: &nbsp;&ldquo;T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi h\u00f4m nay Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 ch\u1ecbu. \u0110i\u1ec1u t\u00f4i vui nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 nhi\u1ec7t t\u00ecnh sang Indonesia \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9. To\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1ea5t c\u1ea3m \u0111\u1ed9ng. C\u1ea3m \u01a1n v\u00ec t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3. V\u00e0 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ni\u1ec1m vinh d\u1ef1 nho nh\u1ecf, l\u00e0 c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean Indonesia c\u0169ng c\u0103ng b\u0103ng r\u00f4n \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam&rdquo;.&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng v\u00e0o ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea1nh tranh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng D s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c - \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean n\u1eb7ng k\u00fd nh\u1ea5t cho chi\u1ebfc HC v\u00e0ng t\u1ea1i Asiad l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.&nbsp;</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal-168-194626.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 Olympic Nepal?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\">HLV Nepal n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/ly-do-gi-khien-olympic-viet-nam-xep-tren-nhat-ban-du-bang-chi-so-tai-asiad-168-194625.html\">L\u00fd do g\u00ec khi\u1ebfn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam x\u1ebfp tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u00f9 b\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 t\u1ea1i ASIAD?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 U23 Nepal (ASIAD 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:11.5pt;font-family:&quot;Roboto-Regular&quot;,&quot;serif&quot;;color:#242424\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5573","checkdouble":"194629"},{"date":"22:25 16/08","title":"HLV Olympic Pakistan chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-olympic-pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chi\u1ec1u 16/8.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><p class=\"MsoNormal\"><span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\">HLV Olympic Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n?<o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ee9 hai \u1edf b\u1ea3ng D g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chi\u1ec1u 16/8, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Jose Antonio Nogueira ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn th\u00eam m\u1ed9t th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i r\u1ea5t \u0111\u1eadm v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 0-4.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Olympic Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Olympic Pakistan n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/14/hlv-pakistan-noi-gi-truoc-cuoc-so-tai-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Olympic Pakistan (gi\u1eefa) \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt\u00a0B\u1ea3n nh\u1ec9nh h\u01a1n Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, nh\u00e0 c\u1ea7m qu\u00e2n ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pakistan v\u1eabn c\u00f2n kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch r\u1ea5t xa v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n do \u0111\u00f3 \u00f4ng kh\u00f4ng b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 gi\u1eefa hai \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, v\u1ecb n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \"Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i r\u1ea5t kh\u00e1c v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111ang l\u00ean nh\u01b0ng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n kinh nghi\u1ec7m h\u01a1n. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt l\u00e0m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t, t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui v\u00ec m\u00ecnh c\u0169ng t\u1eebng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n nh\u1ecf c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i th\u00eam v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo, HLV Olympic Pakistan cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng r\u00e0nh l\u1eafm v\u1ec1 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00e2u \u00c1 nh\u01b0ng m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ed9i U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ec9? C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 l\u1edbn trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u1eeba qua\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ec3 thua c\u1ea3 hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean v\u00e0 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 7 b\u00e0n thua, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0111i ti\u1ebfp g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n v\u1edbi Olympic Pakistan. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i h\u1ecd s\u1ebd c\u00f3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u danh d\u1ef1 v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m Nepal. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra c\u00f9ng gi\u1edd v\u1edbi tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal-168-194626.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal-168-194626.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 Olympic Nepal?</span><br>\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D, ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\">HLV Nepal n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Nepal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 U23 Nepal (ASIAD 2018)</span><br>\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5572","checkdouble":"194630"},{"date":"22:40 16/08","title":"HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u01b0a v\u1ed9i quan t\u00e2m t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/27/hlv-nhat-ban-chua-voi-quan-tam-toi-tran-dau-voi-olympic-viet-nam.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Chia s\u1ebb sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Pakistan, \u00f4ng Hajime Moriyasu \u2013 HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Pakistan.</h2><h2>HLV Hajime Moriyasu ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1edbm t\u1ea1i b\u1ea3ng D, ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i 4-0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan. \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y gi\u00fap h\u1ecd b\u1eaft k\u1ecbp Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, HLV Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec1u th\u1eddi gian n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 r\u1eafn c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan.<br />\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hajime Moriyasu ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hajime Moriyasu ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/27/doi-thu-cua-olympic-viet-nam-thay-doi-nhan-su-truoc-them-asiad-2018.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Hajime Moriyasu ch\u01b0a ngh\u0129 t\u1edbi \u0110T\u00a0Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Moriyasu cho bi\u1ebft: \u201c\u0110\u1ec3 th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Olympic Pakistan, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ed1i m\u1eb7t v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t lo\u1ea1t pha va ch\u1ea1m t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7. C\u00f3 l\u00fac, HLV c\u1ee7a hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn g\u1ea7n nhau \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1ea9u v\u1ec1 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i n\u00f3i v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed3ng nghi\u1ec7p r\u1eb1ng, nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf r\u1ea5t nguy hi\u1ec3m v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft. Th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n c\u1ee7a Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n, ch\u01b0a r\u00f5 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ra sao. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1edd b\u00e1o c\u00e1o t\u1eeb b\u00e1c s\u0129\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u00ednh l\u1ed1i \u0111\u00e1 kh\u00e1 r\u00e1t c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 khi\u1ebfn th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Ryosuke g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. N\u1ebfu th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n n\u00e0y kh\u00f4ng k\u1ecbp b\u00ecnh ph\u1ee5c tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Vi\u1ec7t Nam h\u00f4m 19 t\u1edbi, \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u1ea5t m\u00e1t to l\u1edbn v\u1edbi ng\u01b0\u1eddi Nh\u1eadt.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u00f3i v\u1ec1 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Moriyasu l\u1ea1i cho r\u1eb1ng m\u00ecnh ch\u01b0a h\u1ec1 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u00f9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 nh\u1eefng chuy\u00ean gia Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n d\u1ef1 kh\u00e1n c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cNh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1eb7t m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau \u1edf t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. V\u00ec v\u1eady, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ch\u1ec9 nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u v\u1ec1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay v\u1edbi Pakistan\u201d, \u00f4ng Moriyasu n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h ng\u00e0y 19/8 t\u1edbi. D\u00f9 \u1edf gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y, Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n ch\u1ec9 mang t\u1edbi Indonesia \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu g\u1ed3m nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi 21\u00a0nh\u01b0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Kou Itakura (21 tu\u1ed5i), ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Keita Endo (20 tu\u1ed5i) ho\u1eb7c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Yuto Iwasaki, song \u0111\u00e2y l\u1ea1i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u00f3 t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c v\u00e0 c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng s\u1eafc n\u00e9t.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nTuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng E nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 s\u1eafp t\u1edbi, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo bu\u1ed9c ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf cu\u1ed9c \u0111\u1ecd s\u1ee9c s\u1eafp t\u1edbi.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br />\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\">HLV Nepal n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Nepal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal-168-194626.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/nhung-diem-nhan-chu-y-sau-tran-olympic-viet-nam-20-olympic-nepal-168-194626.html\">Nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n ch\u00fa \u00fd sau tr\u1eadn Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 Olympic Nepal?</span><br />\r\n\u1ede l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai c\u1ee7a b\u1ea3ng D, ASIAD 2018, \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i th\u1ee9 hai v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal. V\u00e0 d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n sau...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 U23 Nepal (ASIAD 2018)</span><br />\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;line-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5571","checkdouble":"194631"},{"date":"23:04 16/08","title":"Gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111i ti\u1ebfp, hai ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i nh\u1eefng g\u00ec?","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/giup-olympic-viet-nam-di-tiep-hai-nguoi-hung-anh-duc-van-duc-da-noi-nhung-gi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i c\u00f9ng t\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng chia s\u1ebb c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau khi t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u00f3 v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u.\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><h2>Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal?</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Olympic Nepal t\u1ed1i 16/8, s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a c\u1eb7p \u0111\u00f4i Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-0, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc 1 l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Anh \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i g\u00ec sau tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng Nepal h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/olympic-viet-nam-nepal-68_zwhr.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>C\u1eb7p Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u2013 V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nepal</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">L\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi ghi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y sau pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u d\u0169ng m\u1ea1nh, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai. Tr\u1eadn th\u1eafng n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1eafc su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng knock-out. T\u00f4i r\u1ea5t h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1ec1 phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u201cTrong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, ai c\u0169ng c\u00f3 quy\u1ec1n chia s\u1ebb \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u v\u00e0 th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho nhau h\u01a1n sau m\u1ed7i \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n l\u1ed7i. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng, c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u00e0 50-50 v\u00e0 t\u00f4i s\u1ebd chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam gi\u00e0nh tr\u1ecdn 9 \u0111i\u1ec3m\u201d, Anh \u0110\u1ee9c n\u00f3i th\u00eam.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c l\u1ea1i t\u1ecf ra ph\u1ea5n kh\u1edfi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Park Hang Seo tr\u1ecdng d\u1ee5ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y. Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 SLNA cho hay: \u201cT\u00f4i th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 r\u1ea5t vui khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV tr\u01b0\u1edfng Park Hang Seo tin t\u01b0\u1edfng cho \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u h\u00f4m nay. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng \u1edf b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n v\u00ec c\u00f2n b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 nhi\u1ec1u t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng quan tr\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. T\u00f4i xin c\u1ea3m \u01a1n anh Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 hai\u201d.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c c\u00f3 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 hai \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o th\u00e0nh b\u00e0n, Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111ang l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi \u0111\u1ea5u hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 nh\u1ea5t trong \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam. Sao tr\u1ebb ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ngh\u1ec7 An c\u0169ng h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u01a1n n\u1eefa n\u1ebfu \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c BHL trao su\u1ea5t \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh trong tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y, Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam s\u1ebd c\u00f3 g\u1ea7n 3 ng\u00e0y ngh\u1ec9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chi\u1ec1u 19/8.</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/video/clip-u23-viet-nam-vs-u23-nepal-20-highlights-325-194624.html\">Video t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: U23 Vi\u1ec7t Nam 2-0 U23 Nepal (ASIAD 2018)</span><br />\r\nTrong l\u1ea7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1 ch\u00ednh c\u00f9ng nhau tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng, c\u1eb7p ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Phan V\u0103n \u0110\u1ee9c vs Nguy\u1ec5n Anh \u0110\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p nh\u1ecbp nh\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br />\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\" /></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\">HLV Nepal n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?</span><br />\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Nepal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-size:16.0pt;\nline-height:115%\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5570","checkdouble":"194632"},{"date":"23:55 16/08","title":"\u201cOlympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng t\u00ednh to\u00e1n nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\u201d","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Vi\u1ec7t Nam","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/olympic-viet-nam-dung-tinh-toan-nhieu-o-tran-gap-nhat-ban.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, c\u1ea3 chuy\u00ean gia V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i l\u1eabn BLV Quang Huy \u0111\u1ec1u kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n t\u00ednh to\u00e1n qu\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.</h2><h2>\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng ch\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 penalty v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\"</h2>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nChi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nepal gi\u00fap \u0110T Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i ng\u00f4i \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng D ngay tr\u00ean Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n do h\u01a1n hi\u1ec7u s\u1ed1 fair-play.</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u1ecb tr\u00ed nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng sau khi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng kh\u00e9p l\u1ea1i, th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i. Trong tr\u01b0\u1eddng h\u1ee3p 2 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eabn h\u00f2a nhau, khi \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea3 hai s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn h\u00e0nh \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ra \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u1ea5t b\u1ea3ng. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ecb tr\u00ed d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u l\u00fac n\u00e0y \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi c\u1ea3 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n l\u1eabn Vi\u1ec7t Nam b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i nh\u00ec b\u1ea3ng n\u00e0y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i g\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ea7u b\u1ea3ng E, nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng l\u00e0 H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. V\u00ec th\u1ebf c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111ang h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf l\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111\u1ea5u cu\u1ed1i.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng ch\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 penalty v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam \u0111\u1eebng ch\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 penalty v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/ndl09109_adks.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam kh\u00f4ng n\u00ean th\u1ee7 h\u00f2a \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u1edd \u0111\u00e1 penalty v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean theo chuy\u00ean gia b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 V\u0169 M\u1ea1nh H\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u00ec th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n toan t\u00ednh nhi\u1ec1u cho tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n. \u00d4ng n\u00f3i: \"T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 v\u1eabn ph\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng th\u00f4i ch\u1ee9 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o penalty th\u00ec may r\u1ee7i. Ch\u00fang ta ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 th\u1eafng h\u1ecd ch\u1ee9 n\u1ebfu t\u00ednh \u0111\u00e1 penalty th\u00ec kh\u00f4ng ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn l\u1eafm.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n th\u1ebf th\u00ec ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Ch\u00fang ta ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd h\u01a1n, c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. Ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00f9i h\u1eb3n v\u1ec1 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 t\u1ea1i VCK U23 ch\u00e2u \u00c1. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t c\u0103ng th\u1eb3ng nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang ta s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng v\u00e0 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c\".<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-va-ket-qua-bong-da-nam-asiad-2018-472-193926.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 nam Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/asiad-2018/lich-thi-dau-u23-viet-nam-ket-qua-tai-asiad-2018-472-193923.html\">L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam t\u1ea1i Asiad 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1ec1 ph\u1ea7n m\u00ecnh, BLV Quang Huy l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 l\u1eddi khen cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u1edbi t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc M\u1eb7t tr\u1eddi m\u1ecdc. Chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean b\u00e1o Tr\u00ed th\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, v\u1ecb BLV n\u00e0y cho hay: \"Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n h\u1ecd b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u n\u00f3ng m\u00e1y d\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea5y, h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u00e0ng v\u00e0o s\u00e2u trong gi\u1ea3i Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd c\u00e0ng ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t, v\u00ec \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 y\u1ebfu th\u00ec kh\u00f3 nh\u1eadn x\u00e9t v\u1ec1 h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 qua t\u1eebng tr\u1eadn, h\u00f4m nay h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 h\u01a1n tr\u1eadn tr\u01b0\u1edbc r\u1ed3i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo t\u00f4i, \u0111\u00e1 v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt c\u00f3 2 c\u00e1ch, 1 l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 lai rai th\u00f4i r\u1ed3i ch\u1edd ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng. Hai l\u00e0 s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 pressing \u0111\u1ec3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u00ec h\u1ecd c\u00f2n non, U21 m\u00e0. T\u00f4i th\u00ec \u1ee7ng h\u1ed9 quan \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ea7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u00e1 pressing lu\u00f4n r\u1ed3i n\u1eafm b\u1eaft th\u1eddi c\u01a1 \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean v\u1edbi Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n, ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1eef t\u00e2m th\u1ebf h\u00f2a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, v\u00ec h\u00f2a th\u00ec ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00e1 penalty n\u00ean v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n quy\u1ebft th\u1eafng th\u00f4i. T\u00f4i v\u1eabn gi\u1eef ni\u1ec1m tin \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1eafng Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u00e0 Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 16h00. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f4ng mang theo \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh m\u1ea1nh nh\u1ea5t, c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Vi\u1ec7t Nam c\u1ea7n ch\u01a1i t\u1eadp trung, t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e1 h\u1ebft m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u01b0\u1edbng t\u1edbi m\u1ed9t chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng ngay trong 90 ph\u00fat.<br>\r\n<span style=\"font-size: 13pt; font-family: \" times=\"\" new=\"\" roman\",=\"\" serif;=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" -0.25pt;\"=\"\"><o:p></o:p></span></p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-nhat-ban-168-194630.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/14/hlv-olympic-pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-olympic-pakistan-noi-gi-ve-tran-viet-nam-vs-nhat-ban-168-194630.html\">HLV Olympic Pakistan chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Vi\u1ec7t Nam vs Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nHLV Olympic Pakistan \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u01b0a ra nh\u1eefng ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh sau tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n chi\u1ec1u 16/8.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-park-hang-seo-tu-tin-o-tran-gap-olympic-nhat-ban-168-194629.html\">HLV Park Hang Seo t\u1ef1 tin \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Olympic Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong bu\u1ed5i h\u1ecdp b\u00e1o sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Nepal, HLV Park Hang Seo cho bi\u1ebft m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 c\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua Nh\u1eadt B\u1ea3n.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-viet-nam/hlv-nepal-het-loi-khen-ngoi-thay-tro-park-hang-seo-sau-tran-dau-168-194628.html\">HLV Nepal n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u?</span><br>\r\nChia s\u1ebb sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Olympic Vi\u1ec7t Nam, HLV Nepal \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn tr\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a th\u1ea7y tr\u00f2 Park Hang Seo.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"MsoNormal\" style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div>\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5569","checkdouble":"194633"},{"date":"21:42 16/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 16/8: Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp M.U","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/6/diem-tin-toi-168-fred-tiet-lo-ly-do-gia-nhap-mu.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp M.U, Messi \u0111\u01b0a ra l\u1eddi h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n v\u1edbi Barca, Bayern b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm sao Tottenham,... l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt trong \u0111i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 16/8.</h2><h2>Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp M.U</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t chia s\u1ebb m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, ch\u00e2n s\u00fat ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil \u0111\u00e3 ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do chuy\u1ec3n t\u1edbi thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 s\u00e2n Old Trafford.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fred t\u00e2m s\u1ef1: \u201cC\u1ea3 Manchester City v\u00e0 PSG \u0111\u1ec1u li\u00ean h\u1ec7 v\u1edbi t\u00f4i nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ch\u1ecdn United. T\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi Giberto Silva, c\u1ef1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Arsenal. Anh \u1ea5y n\u00f3i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i r\u1eb1ng Man United l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u0129 \u0111\u1ea1i. T\u00f4i c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i chuy\u1ec7n v\u1edbi gia \u0111\u00ecnh t\u00f4i v\u00e0 t\u00f4i nh\u00ecn th\u1ea5y c\u1ea3m x\u00fac tr\u00ean g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 m\u00ecnh \u0111\u00e3 l\u1ef1a ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u00fang. T\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng \u1edf gi\u1ea3i Ngo\u1ea1i h\u1ea1ng Anh, \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u hay nh\u1ea5t th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi.\u201d<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 168 Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 168 Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp MU h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/6/sao-tre-khang-dinh-se-giup-do-tan-binh-fred-cua-mu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Fred gia nh\u1eadp M.U m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n l\u00e0 d\u1ef1a v\u00e0o l\u1eddi khuy\u00ean c\u1ee7a Giberto Silva</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>Messi h\u1ee9a mang danh hi\u1ec7u Champions League th\u1ee9 6 cho Barca<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u trong ng\u00e0y ra m\u1eaft vai tr\u00f2 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng c\u1ee7a Barca, Leo Messi h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd l\u00e0m t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch Champions League.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">El Pulga chia s\u1ebb: \u201cT\u00f4i h\u1ee9a s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ec3 mang ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch \u0111\u00f3 [Champions League] v\u1ec1 SV\u0110 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed1i v\u1edbi t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 1 vinh d\u1ef1 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi [\u0111eo b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng]. T\u00f4i bi\u1ebft nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m trong vai tr\u00f2 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 th\u1eadt tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi khi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u1ed1i ti\u1ebfp Puyol, Xavi v\u00e0 Iniesta\".<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Chelsea r\u00e1o ri\u1ebft t\u00ecm gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u0129 thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng Man Utd, nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u01b0u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y ch\u00ednh l\u00e0 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u0129 thu\u1eadt m\u1edbi k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi Michael Emenalo ra \u0111i h\u1ed3i th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Vi\u1ec7c kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u0129 thu\u1eadt khi\u1ebfn m\u1ecdi v\u1ea5n \u0111\u1ec1 li\u00ean quan \u0111\u1ebfn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Chelsea trong hai \u201cphi\u00ean ch\u1ee3\u201d g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec1u do gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u00e0nh Marina Granovskaia \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m. Tuy nhi\u00ean, vi\u1ec7c HLV Maurizio Sarri mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi chuy\u00ean tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u1ea3m nhi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng t\u00e1c chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 gi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c k\u0129 thu\u1eadt tr\u1edf n\u00ean c\u1ea5p thi\u1ebft v\u1edbi The Blues.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Real s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng mua c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u00f9 m\u1ea5t Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Julen Lopetegui kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u1edf Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u v\u1eeba qua s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh s\u00e1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nh\u1eefng k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ea1ch ra c\u1ee7a CLB s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng thay \u0111\u1ed5i b\u1edfi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft n\u00e0y. B\u00e2y gi\u1edd La Liga m\u1edbi b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u, \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 danh hi\u1ec7u quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi ch\u00fang t\u00f4i v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u t\u1ed1t\u201d, t\u00e2n thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Los Blancos chia s\u1ebb.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Modric mu\u1ed1n sang Italia<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a Sky Sports Italia cho bi\u1ebft, h\u00f4m nay Luka Modric c\u00f9ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n s\u1ebd g\u1eb7p m\u1eb7t BL\u0110 Real Madrid \u0111\u1ec3 xin \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n sang Inter Milan. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, Los Blancos v\u1eabn t\u1ecf ra c\u1ee9ng r\u1eafn khi nh\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft kh\u00f4ng \u201cbu\u00f4ng\u201d ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Croatia tr\u1eeb khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 750 tri\u1ec7u euro ph\u00ed gi\u1ea3i ph\u00f3ng h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng c\u1ee7a anh.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>T\u1edbi l\u01b0\u1ee3t Lukaku \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u1ecf kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb \u0110TQG sau EURO 2020<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1ea3 l\u1eddi trong b\u00e0i ph\u1ecfng v\u1ea5n m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t v\u1edbi t\u1edd Business Insider, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Romelu Lukaku \u0111\u00e3 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn anh \u0111ang xem x\u00e9t \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng chia tay \u0110T B\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ec3 t\u1eadp trung cho M.U. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0y chia s\u1ebb: \u201cSau k\u1ef3 EURO t\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, t\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m ph\u00f9 h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i\u201d. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lukaku \u0111ang l\u00e0 ch\u00e2n s\u00fat s\u1ed1 1 c\u1ee7a Man \u0111\u1ecf l\u00fac n\u00e0y. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc anh \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 51 tr\u1eadn v\u00e0 ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 27 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>De Bruyne c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 3 th\u00e1ng v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Theo ngu\u1ed3n tin c\u1ee7a City Watch, De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u g\u1ed1i nghi\u00eam tr\u1ecdng trong bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp h\u00f4m th\u1ee9 4. Nhi\u1ec1u kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb t\u1ed5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng v\u00e0 c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb 2 \u0111\u1ebfn 3 th\u00e1ng t\u1edbi. Trong qu\u00e1 kh\u1ee9, De Bruyne t\u1eebng g\u1eb7p ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Everton v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 1 n\u0103m 2016. \u1ede th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u00f3, De Bruyne \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i ng\u1ed3i ngo\u00e0i h\u01a1n 2 th\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tin kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 x\u1ea5u h\u01a1n v\u1edbi Man City b\u1edfi l\u1ebd De Bruyne \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c xem l\u00e0 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Pep Guardiola. M\u00f9a tr\u01b0\u1edbc, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 27 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 52 tr\u1eadn cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o xanh tr\u00ean m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 12 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 21 b\u00e0n kh\u00e1c.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Bayern b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd nh\u1eafm sao Tottenham<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong m\u1ed9t di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn m\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y, CLB Bayern Munich \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 m\u1eaft t\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Toby Alderweireld c\u1ee7a CLB Tottenham. N\u1ebfu b\u00e1n Jerome Boateng, Bayern Munich s\u1ebd t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Alderweireld. D\u00f9 v\u1eady, t\u00ednh kh\u1ea3 thi c\u1ee7a th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng cao b\u1edfi th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng Premier League \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda n\u00ean Tottenham s\u1ebd kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng nh\u1ea3 trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi B\u1ec9 trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u00ecm s\u1ef1 thay th\u1ebf x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Juve quy\u1ebft gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Pjanic <o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eb1m gi\u1eef ch\u00e2n Miralem Pjanic tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 nh\u00f2m ng\u00f3 c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c \u00f4ng l\u1edbn ch\u00e2u \u00c2u nh\u01b0 Real Madrid hay Man City, CLB Juventus \u0111ang l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch gia h\u1ea1n h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Bosnia, Miralem Pjani\u0107. Theo \u0111\u00f3, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i n\u00e0y s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn m\u1ee9c l\u01b0\u01a1ng 7 tri\u1ec7u euro/m\u00f9a (t\u0103ng 2,5 tri\u1ec7u so v\u1edbi hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i) v\u00e0 k\u00e9o d\u00e0i giao k\u00e8o \u0111\u1ebfn th\u00e1ng 6/2022.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nXEM TH\u00caM:\u00a0<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-vi-man-utd-zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-juventus-184-194555.html\" target=\"_blank\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/8: V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus</span></p>\r\nMinh Long (TTVN)</div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5568","checkdouble":"194627"},{"date":"06:07 17/08","title":"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8: Barca ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ti\u1ec1m n\u0103ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/17/diem-tin-bong-da-24h-sang-ngay-178-barca-chinh-thuc-chia-tay-hau-ve-tiem-nang.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u00ean trang B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h t\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8.</h2><h2>Sassuolo chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 sao Barca\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 178 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 178 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>\u0110i\u1ec3m tin B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h s\u00e1ng ng\u00e0y 17/8:&nbsp;Barca chia tay h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marlon</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\nBarcelona  v\u00e0 Sassuolo \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ea1t th\u1ecfa thu\u1eadn chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Marlon Santos. \u0110\u1ed9i  b\u00f3ng Serie A s\u1ebd tr\u1ea3 6 tri\u1ec7u euro cho Barca \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1eef k\u00fd c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7  n\u00e0y. Barca c\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u kho\u1ea3n mua l\u1ea1i Marlon v\u00e0 h\u01b0\u1edfng 50% s\u1ed1 ti\u1ec1n chuy\u1ec3n  nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu Sassuolo b\u00e1n c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Brazil sau n\u00e0y. N\u1ebfu Marlon ch\u01a1i \u0111\u1ee7  50 tr\u1eadn th\u00ec Sassuolo s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i tr\u1ea3 th\u00eam cho Barca 6 tri\u1ec7u euro n\u1eefa.\r\n<h2>Modric mu\u1ed1n chuy\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ebfn Inter</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Calcio Mercato kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Luka Modric \u0111ang mong mu\u1ed1n \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Inter. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Vlado Lemic \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 li\u00ean h\u1ec7 tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Florentino Perez \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap ng\u00f4i sao 32 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ra \u0111i. D\u1eabu v\u1eady, th\u1ecb tr\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng \u1edf Italia s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng c\u1eeda trong 24 gi\u1edd t\u1edbi v\u00e0 th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 n\u00e0y kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng. Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n m\u1ea5t th\u00eam 1 si\u00eau sao sau khi \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec3 Cristiano Ronaldo t\u1edbi Juventus.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Mavididi s\u1eafp \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho Juventus</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd The Sun kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Stephy Mavididi c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111ang chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 Italia l\u00e0 Juventus. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 20 tu\u1ed5i ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o cho \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t Arsenal. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb g\u1eedi cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n 3 l\u1ea7n k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi k\u00fd h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng chuy\u00ean nghi\u1ec7p v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng th\u00e0nh London n\u0103m 2015.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sao tr\u1ebb Arsenal gia nh\u1eadp Charlton</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Krystian Bielik \u0111\u00e3 gia nh\u1eadp Charlton Athletic theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i. Trung v\u1ec7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ba Lan gia nh\u1eadp Arsenal t\u1eeb n\u0103m 2015 nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1ed9t. <br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Leeds nh\u1eafm sao Liverpool</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd Yorkshire Evening Post \u0111\u01b0a tin Leeds \u0111ang t\u00ednh chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 ng\u00f4i sao Marko Grujic c\u1ee7a Liverpool n\u1ebfu kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea1t th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng \u1edf th\u01b0\u01a1ng v\u1ee5 Muhamed Besic. N\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, Grujic \u0111\u00e3 d\u00e0nh c\u1ea3 m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i cho Cardiff City theo d\u1ea1ng cho m\u01b0\u1ee3n v\u00e0 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y th\u0103ng h\u1ea1ng l\u00ean Premier League.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Sporting b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd mu\u1ed1n c\u00f3 Terry</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">T\u1edd A Bola cho bi\u1ebft John Terry \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh m\u1ee5c ti\u00eau c\u1ee7a Sporting. C\u1ef1u \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Chelsea hi\u1ec7n \u0111ang kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ea7u qu\u00e2n cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o sau khi h\u1ebft h\u1ee3p \u0111\u1ed3ng v\u1edbi Aston Villa cu\u1ed1i m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i. Terry \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eb7p Madeira Rodrigues, m\u1ed9t \u1ee9ng c\u1eed vi\u00ean cho chi\u1ebfc gh\u1ebf ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Sporting. Hai b\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e0m ph\u00e1n v\u1ec1 m\u1ed9t v\u1ee5 chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng n\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Rodrigues gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng trong cu\u1ed9c b\u1ea7u ch\u1ecdn ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Sporting h\u00f4m 7/9 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng m\u1ee5c \u0111i\u1ec3m tin kh\u00e1c c\u1ee7a B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 24h:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-toi-168-fred-tiet-lo-ly-do-gia-nhap-mu-184-194627.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin t\u1ed1i 16/8: Fred ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 l\u00fd do gia nh\u1eadp M.U</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/diem-tin-bong-da-toi-158-vi-man-utd-zidane-san-sang-lat-keo-juventus-184-194555.html\">\u0110i\u1ec3m tin b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 t\u1ed1i 15/8: V\u00ec Man Utd, Zidane s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng l\u1eadt k\u00e8o Juventus</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Bongda24h.vn (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5567","checkdouble":"194638"},{"date":"18:57 16/08","title":"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 TBN","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/16/3-ly-do-khien-real-madrid-tro-thanh-cuu-vuong-o-sieu-cup-chau-au.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn thua 4-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid c\u0169ng l\u00e0 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tranh ng\u00f4i v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch c\u1ee7a CLB Real Madrid trong su\u1ed1t 18 n\u0103m qua. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00e2u l\u00e0 nguy\u00ean nh\u00e2n d\u1eabn t\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 n\u00e0y?\r\n\r\n\r\n</h2><br>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng x\u00e1o tr\u1ed9n l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng</h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh Real Madrid kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n ch\u00e2n s\u00fat n\u00e0o c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi 30 b\u00e0n trong m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i nh\u01b0 Ronaldo, c\u00f2n t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Luka Modric c\u0169ng \u0111ang \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1eb7t d\u1ea5u h\u1ecfi khi anh \u0111ang c\u00f3 k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch chuy\u1ec3n sang Serie A th\u00ec chuy\u1ec7n Real \u0111\u1ec3 thua Atletico c\u0169ng l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng nh\u1eefng th\u1ebf, nh\u1eefng g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t c\u00f2n l\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a Real c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 sung s\u1ee9c cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y. Raphael Varane \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u d\u01b0\u1edbi s\u1ee9c d\u00f9 anh v\u1eeba gi\u00e0nh ch\u1ee9c v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup c\u00f9ng \u0110T Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Real Madrid tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/12fd3-1534394552-800.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau cup ch\u00e2u \u00c2u</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 3-2, ch\u00ednh Raphael Varane \u0111\u00e3 m\u1eafc l\u1ed7i l\u1edbn khi \u0111\u1ec3 Partey c\u01b0\u1edbp \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00f3ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi chuy\u1ec1n v\u00e0o cho Saul d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m tung n\u00f3c l\u01b0\u1edbi Real.\u00a0<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p c\u1ee7a Raphael Varane l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i b\u00e0n c\u00e3i nh\u01b0ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi v\u1eeba tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i sau k\u1ef3 ngh\u1ec9 h\u00e8 v\u1eeba qua, s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u1ec3 Varane thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ed1t trong su\u1ed1t 120 ph\u00fat \u1edf c\u01b0\u1eddng \u0111\u1ed9 cao, nh\u1ea5t l\u00e0 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c b\u1ec1n b\u1ec9 nh\u01b0 Atletico Madrid.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 Varane, Marcelo c\u0169ng c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico. Ch\u00ednh b\u1edfi Marcelo c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ee9u b\u00f3ng thay v\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111i h\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng bi\u00ean d\u1ecdc, Atletico m\u1edbi t\u00ecm \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2 do c\u00f4ng c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Diego Costa \u1edf ph\u00fat 79. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3, \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia d\u1ed3n \u00e9p \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd ti\u1ebfng c\u00f2i m\u00e3n cu\u1ed9c vang l\u00ean.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<h2>Asensio kh\u00f3 l\u00f2ng th\u1ebf ch\u1ed7 Ronaldo<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi chia tay C.Ronaldo sang Juventus, Real t\u1ecf ra kh\u00e1 b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n tr\u00ean TTCN thay v\u00ec s\u1ed1t s\u1eafng chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 m\u1ed9t ch\u00e2n s\u00fat \u0111\u1eaft gi\u00e1 thay th\u1ebf CR7. S\u1edf d\u0129 c\u00f3 chuy\u1ec7n n\u00e0y b\u1edfi h\u1ecd tin t\u01b0\u1edfng v\u00e0o t\u00e0i n\u0103ng c\u1ee7a Marco Asensio c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 kh\u1ecfa l\u1ea5p \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng kho\u1ea3ng tr\u1ed1ng c\u1ee7a CR7 t\u1ea1i Real.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00eam qua, l\u1ea1i ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111i\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i. Asensio \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n ngh\u00e8o n\u00e8n tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi b\u1ecb thay ra \u1edf ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 56. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 anh kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ea1i nhi\u1ec1u d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n chuy\u00ean m\u00f4n tr\u01b0\u1edbc s\u1ef1 theo k\u00e8m s\u00e1t sao c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Atletico. R\u00f5 r\u00e0ng Real c\u1ea7m b\u1ed5 sung th\u00eam m\u1ed9t g\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u1eb7t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng n\u1ebfu mu\u1ed1n chinh ph\u1ee5c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Asensio\" title=\"Asensio\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/Asensio.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>Asensio c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00e1ng qu\u00ean tr\u01b0\u1edb Atletico Madrid</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2>HLV Lopetegui c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian<o:p></o:p></h2>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00eam qua, CLB Real Madrid \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 2-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch c\u00f9ng th\u00e0nh ph\u1ed1 Atletico Madrid trong tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018. Tr\u1eadn thua n\u00e0y v\u1eabn c\u00f2n qu\u00e1 s\u1edbm \u0111\u1ec3 k\u1ebft lu\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Ho\u00e0ng gia \u0111\u00e3 sai l\u1ea7m khi \u0111\u1eb7t ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o t\u00e2n HLV Julen Lopetegui, ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang t\u1edbi th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng cho Real sau th\u1eddi Zidane.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Song r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng, Lopetegui v\u1eabn c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 hi\u1ec3u h\u01a1n v\u1ec1 c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Real. \u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid, Lopetegui \u0111\u00e3 y\u00eau c\u1ea7u Bale v\u00e0 Asensio \u0111\u00f3ng \u0111inh \u1edf 2 b\u00ean c\u00e1nh, trong khi Kroos kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ph\u00e9p r\u1eddi v\u1ecb tr\u00ed v\u00f2ng tr\u00f2n trung t\u00e2m.<br>\r\n<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Lopetegui\" title=\"Lopetegui\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/c4b30-1534393070-800.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td><em>HLV Lopetegui v\u1eabn c\u00f2n nhi\u1ec1u vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m t\u1ea1i Real</em></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y \u0111\u00e3 l\u00e0m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf t\u1edbi Marcelo, m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch tham gia t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng nh\u01b0ng 'ng\u1ea1i' k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p ph\u00f2ng th\u1ee7. M\u1ecdi h\u1ec7 lu\u1ef5 \u0111\u00e3 d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn s\u1ef1 b\u1ebf t\u1eafc trong nh\u1eefng pha l\u00ean b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Real Madrid. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Isco m\u1ea5t \u0111i s\u1ef1 s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o v\u1ed1n c\u00f3 v\u1edbi tr\u00e1i b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 \u0111ang tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 h\u00ecnh d\u1ea1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 's\u1ed1 8' nh\u01b0 th\u1eddi c\u00f2n thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho Malaga, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c l\u00e3ng ph\u00ed.<o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u00ean c\u1ea1nh \u0111\u00f3, m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u d\u1ec5 nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5y \u1edf tr\u1eadn n\u00e0y l\u00e0 Real ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng b\u1ed5ng kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u v\u00e0 d\u00f9 c\u00f3 mang v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y nh\u01b0ng \u0111\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u1ed1i ch\u01a1i th\u01b0\u1eddng th\u1ea5y c\u1ee7a Real. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady, c\u00e1c C\u0110V Real c\u0169ng c\u1ea7n th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho Real b\u1edfi hi\u1ec7n gi\u1edd h\u1ecd v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c, trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 v\u1eabn \u0111ang ph\u1ea3i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m quen v\u1edbi h\u1ec7 th\u1ed1ng chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt c\u1ee7a v\u1ecb thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng m\u1edbi. <o:p></o:p></p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico Madrid d\u1eabu sao c\u0169ng m\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u1edfi \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ed9t m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Los Blancos. V\u00e0 n\u1ebfu c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i, h\u1ecd ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chinh ph\u1ee5c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng danh hi\u1ec7u \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i 2018/19.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</p>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-tran-tranh-sieu-cup-chau-au-2018-184-194606.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau C\u00fap Ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018</span><br>\r\nSau bi\u1ebft bao n\u1ed7i \u0111au tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1eddng ch\u00e2u l\u1ee5c, Atletico Madrid cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea7n n\u00e0o \u0111\u00f3 ph\u1ee5c th\u00f9 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng h\u00e0ng x\u00f3m k\u00ecnh \u0111\u1ecbch Real Madrid v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/7/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-tbn/sep-real-len-tieng-ve-tuong-lai-modric-180-194607.html\">S\u1ebfp Real l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng v\u1ec1 t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai Modric</span><br>\r\nGi\u00e1m \u0111\u1ed1c Emilio Butragueno c\u1ee7a Real kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh Modric \u0111ang h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac t\u1ea1i Bernabeu, qua \u0111\u00f3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t m\u1ecdi tin \u0111\u1ed3n xung quanh t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-184-194585.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/real-madrid-thua-atletico-madrid-khi-nhung-noi-nho-cu-day-them-184-194585.html\">Real Madrid g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Atletico: Khi nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7i nh\u1edb c\u1ee9 d\u00e0y th\u00eam</span><br>\r\nN\u1ed7i nh\u1edb l\u00e0 t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta nh\u1eafc \u0111\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u nh\u1ea5t sau tr\u1eadn tranh Si\u00eau c\u00fap ch\u00e2u \u00c2u 2018, Real Madrid d\u01b0\u1edbi tri\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ea1i Julen Lopetegui ch\u1ec9 sau m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ed9 r\u00f5...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Minh Long (TTVN)<span style=\"font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><o:p></o:p></span></p></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5566","checkdouble":"194621"},{"date":"18:17 16/08","title":"Sao tr\u1ebb ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Arsenal m\u1ea5t h\u1ebft h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 tr\u00e1i","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/8/16/arsenal-don-tin-du-tu-sao-tre-maitlandniles.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Arsenal kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh sao tr\u1ebb Ainsley Maitland-Niles s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi th\u00e1ng 10 v\u00ec ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb Ainsley Maitland-Niles \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft n\u1ee9t nh\u1ecf \u1edf x\u01b0\u01a1ng ch\u00e2n sau pha va ch\u1ea1m v\u1edbi Kyle Walker trong tr\u1eadn khai m\u1ea1c Premier League v\u1edbi Man City. Ngay sau t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u00f4ng b\u00e1o tr\u00ean trang ch\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a Arsenal cho bi\u1ebft: <em>\u201cAinsley \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1ed9t v\u1ebft n\u1ee9t nh\u1ecf \u1edf x\u01b0\u01a1ng m\u00e1c. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1eeb kho\u1ea3ng 6 \u0111\u1ebfn 8 tu\u1ea7n\u201d.<br>\r\n</em><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Maitland-Niles ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Arsenal lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Sao tr\u1ebb Maitland-Niles ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng n\u1eb7ng, Arsenal lo s\u1ed1t v\u00f3 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/16/arsenal-don-tin-du-tu-sao-tre-maitlandniles.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Sao tr\u1ebb Maitland-Niles ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Man City</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHuy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i David Seaman th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng Maitland-Niles \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Man City khi b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp v\u00e0 khai th\u00e1c qu\u00e1 th\u01b0\u1eddng xuy\u00ean.<br>\r\n<em><br>\r\n\u201cCh\u00fang ta c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 thi\u1ebfu t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c \u1edf h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 Arsenal. T\u00f4i th\u1ea5y th\u00f4ng c\u1ea3m cho Maitland-Niles. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb c\u00f4 l\u1eadp ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cRiyad Mahrez v\u00e0 Kyle Walker t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00e1 \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n. V\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 b\u1edfi b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 n\u00e0o kh\u00e1c.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrung v\u1ec7 Carl Jenkinson c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c cho l\u00e0 s\u1ebd ph\u1ea3i ngh\u1ec9 thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng th\u1eddi gian t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 nh\u01b0 Maitland-Niles. Anh \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb gi\u00e3n d\u00e2y ch\u1eb1ng m\u1eaft c\u00e1 v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i trong m\u1ed9t th\u1eddi gian ng\u1eafn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNh\u1eefng ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng d\u00e0i h\u1ea1n c\u1ee7a Sead Kolasinac v\u00e0 Laurent Koscielny l\u1ea1i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn nh\u1eefng t\u00edn hi\u1ec7u t\u00edch c\u1ef1c. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y s\u1ebd l\u1ea7n l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 10 v\u00e0 th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m nay.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u00e1o th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng x\u00e1c nh\u1eadn r\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 Nacho Monreal v\u00e0 Danny Welbeck \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i t\u1eadp luy\u1ec7n. N\u1ebfu m\u1ecdi chuy\u1ec7n ti\u1ebfn tri\u1ec3n t\u1ed1t th\u00ec c\u1ea3 hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec1u c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t trong tr\u1eadn derby London v\u1edbi Chelsea cu\u1ed1i tu\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Arsenal:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/tan-hlv-arsenal-bi-chi-trich-hoc-doi-man-city-172-194568.html\">T\u00e2n HLV Arsenal b\u1ecb ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch h\u1ecdc \u0111\u00f2i Man City</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/sao-arsenal-tu-sanh-minh-voi-ronaldo-va-salah-172-194565.html\">Sao Arsenal t\u1ef1 s\u00e1nh m\u00ecnh v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Salah</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5565","checkdouble":"194616"},{"date":"06:39 17/08","title":"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i t\u00e2n binh \"bom t\u1ea5n\" c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i Dennis Wise khen ng\u1ee3i Jorginho h\u1ebft l\u1eddi v\u00e0 kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh m\u1ed1i quan h\u1ec7 gi\u1eefa c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y v\u00e0 HLV Sarri s\u1ebd gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Dennis Wise l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i theo d\u00f5i nh\u1eefng b\u01b0\u1edbc ti\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a Chelsea \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y r\u1ea5t s\u00e1t sao. \u00d4ng th\u1eadm ch\u00ed \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eadn n\u01a1i theo d\u00f5i m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a The Blues trong giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi gia nh\u1eadp Chelsea c\u00f9ng HLV Sarri t\u1eeb Napoli, Jorginho \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng ngay l\u1eadp t\u1ee9c. Anh ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m penalty trong tr\u1eadn ra m\u1eaft Premier League, gi\u00fap Chelsea \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Huddersfield v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 chung cu\u1ed9c l\u00e0 3-0.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho c\u1ee7a Chelsea h\u1ebft l\u1eddi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/8/17/huyen-thoai-khen-ngoi-tan-binh-bom-tan-cua-chelsea-het-loi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Dennis Wise khen ng\u1ee3i ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Jorginho</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cT\u00f4i r\u1ea5t th\u00edch c\u1eadu b\u00e9 m\u00e0 Sarri \u0111\u00e3 mang v\u1ec1. T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 Jorginho thi \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 theo d\u00f5i c\u1eadu \u1ea5y v\u00e0 c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y che l\u1ea5p nh\u1eefng l\u1ed7 h\u1ed5ng, c\u00e1ch c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u00e1p s\u00e1t v\u00e0 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 \u0111i\u1ec1u ti\u1ebft nh\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cV\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c \u0111\u01b0a v\u1ec1 Jorginho, Chelsea \u0111\u00e3 chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi r\u1ea5t hi\u1ec3u Sarri. Khi b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u1edf v\u1ecb tr\u00ed ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 trung t\u00e2m hi\u1ec3u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00e1ch ch\u01a1i c\u1ee7a HLV v\u00e0 truy\u1ec1n t\u1ea3i \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 t\u1edbi m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00ec c\u1eadu \u1ea5y th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 h\u1eefu d\u1ee5ng. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u01b0\u1eddi c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 c\u1eadu \u1ea5y \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb m\u1ea5t b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n trong su\u1ed1t giai \u0111o\u1ea1n giao h\u1eefu. T\u00f4i th\u1eadt s\u1ef1 \u0111ang r\u1ea5t mong ch\u1edd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ea5y c\u1eadu \u1ea5y ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n \u1edf m\u00f9a gi\u1ea3i n\u00e0y\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\nJorginho \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Chelsea chi\u00eau m\u1ed9 h\u00e8 n\u00e0y v\u1edbi m\u1ee9c ph\u00ed chuy\u1ec3n nh\u01b0\u1ee3ng l\u00ean \u0111\u1ebfn 50 tri\u1ec7u b\u1ea3ng. Anh s\u1ebd \u0111\u00f3ng vai tr\u00f2 quan tr\u1ecdng d\u01b0\u1edbi th\u1eddi Sarri khi l\u00e0 ng\u01b0\u1eddi hi\u1ec3u r\u00f5 nh\u1ea5t chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt Sarri-ball trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh Chelsea.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 Chelsea:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-anh/zaha-bao-tin-buon-cho-chelsea-172-194549.html\">H\u00e0ng th\u1ea3i MU b\u00e1o tin bu\u1ed3n cho Chelsea</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/bong-da-chau-au/bakayoko-tri-an-chelsea-sau-khi-gia-nhap-ac-milan-184-194523.html\">Bakayoko tri \u00e2n Chelsea sau khi gia nh\u1eadp AC Milan</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"5564","checkdouble":"194639"}]}